three days after a patch, tempers might flare.  But as long as naggy goes down on patch day, I don't see too many people objecting.  I could be very wrong, there could be some serious objections, but it was worth a shot <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </font><P><p><img src="http://www.noble-blade.net/images/logo.gif" align="left">Raifin<br>Warrior of The Rathe<br><a href="http://www.noble-blade.net">Noble Blade</a><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE>